UI Design & Inpiration: 

Dribbble – A popular platform for designers to showcase their work, including UX/UI design, web design, and illustrations. It serves as a hub for inspiration, where professionals share creative concepts, animations, and design trends
https://dribbble.com/


Behance – A platform by Adobe that allows designers, artists, and creatives to publish their portfolios. It features diverse design ideas, including branding, graphic design, web design, and UX/UI projects, making it a great source for inspiration
https://www.behance.net/search/projects/ideas

Mobbin – A curated library of the latest mobile app UI patterns, offering detailed screenshots and flow designs from real-world applications. It helps designers analyze trends, explore best practices, and streamline their design process for mobile applications.
https://mobbin.com/